imdb.plot outline: Lindsay the Nostalgia Chick is here to review those nostalgic films that appeal to the female audience. While she started out being the feminine version of The Nostalgia Critic, Lindsay has since broken off into her own wild and wacky review series that includes her best friend Nella turning to the "Dark" side.
